# Hydroseed Inc. Premium Redesign Demo (Astro)

This repository contains a complete outreach/demo redesign for **Hydroseed Inc.**, focused on hydroseeding, lawn installation, erosion control, and post-installation support across Greater Michiana.

## Stack used
- **Astro** for fast static pages and strong SEO output.
- **Custom CSS design system** in `src/styles/global.css` for premium, easy-to-edit styling.

> Why Astro: excellent performance, SEO-friendly static output, simple component architecture, and easy deployment to Vercel/Replit.

## Project goals implemented
- Premium local-service design with contractor-grade credibility.
- Conversion-focused quote path with repeat CTAs, click-to-call, and sticky mobile quote button.
- Unique service/location pages and local-intent internal linking.
- Structured SEO metadata and JSON-LD schema helpers.
- Intentional image placeholder system ready for replacement with approved project photos.

